Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:08.29,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're going to begin the match\Nbetween Class 1 and Class 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:13.80,sign_1703_2_Sports_Day,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Sports Day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:13.80,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sports Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:17.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.16,0:01:18.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:20.14,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:27.58,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yamane-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:29.57,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,G-Go get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:30.65,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kurihara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:33.11,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I-I want to go home and sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:38.91,Default,Other Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Takase!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:41.84,Italics,Other Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Is it too obvious I like him\Nif I cheer for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:43.66,Default,Other Other Girl,0000,0000,0000,,C-Class 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.11,0:01:48.26,Italics,Other Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be too obvious I like Kanda\Nif I look at her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:02.16,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Furuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:06.86,Default,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:09.94,sign_3033_16_Class_4,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Class 4
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:09.94,sign_3033_17_Class_1,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Class 1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:09.94,Default,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Goda!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:12.73,Default,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's down to you guys and us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:13.37,Default,Brown,0000,0000,0000,,Noro...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:14.50,Default,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:16.38,Default,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, no one with a girlfriend—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:18.02,Default,Brown,0000,0000,0000,,You're handling too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:19.35,Default,Brown,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make the next match?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:22.74,Default,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I can't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:23.87,Default,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:25.22,Default,Brown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know the rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:25.60,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's clean this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:26.45,Default,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:25.98,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:26.45,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:28.44,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki, next match is the final, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:29.68,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:30.71,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:33.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kana, make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:35.36,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:37.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,L-Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:38.68,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki, you ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:43.50,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Keisuke, I want to play in boys' soccer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:44.92,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.92,0:02:45.86,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You can play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:46.99,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Ask someone to switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:47.86,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:48.98,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,But who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:50.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Keisuke, switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:54.86,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're starting the final match.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:56.98,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Class 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:59.10,Default,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,Goda's mine, Takase!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:00.70,Default,Other guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Just don't handle the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:02.70,Default,Girls and Keisuke,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Class 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:04.46,Default,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,You got this, goalie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:05.24,Default,Gouda,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:08.33,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.08,Default,Left girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sugawara-kun's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:20.11,Default,Right girl,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:21.02,Default,Left girl,0000,0000,0000,,Look, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:21.84,Default,Right girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.14,Default,Left girl,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:25.35,Default,Right girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you telling me, Yo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.96,0:03:29.59,Italics,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,Takano, are you watching me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:31.80,Italics,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, why haven't I let go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:33.37,Italics,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,I don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.25,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:56.96,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:04:01.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was just trying to get the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.55,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It would have been ours\Nif you hadn't touched it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:05.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please, I helped you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:06.97,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your help, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.82,Default,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Chiaki? Lovers' quarrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:09.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:10.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:12.36,Default,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, all this flirting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:13.89,Default,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,All you bastards with girlfriends...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:15.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The ball wasn't out of play.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:18.16,Default,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:32.91,Default,Blue,0000,0000,0000,,Class 4 is going to lose at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.16,Default,Blue,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all cheer for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:35.33,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:37.58,Default,Blue,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:40.59,Default,Blue,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Class 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.47,Default,Blue,0000,0000,0000,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:45.93,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Kana isn't cheering for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.30,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what can I expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.56,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We've broken up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.43,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:55.74,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Quit screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:57.44,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:59.80,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.32,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You call that cheering?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:05.32,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Impress me, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:10.08,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:21.55,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, Kana, you aren't even\Nmy girlfriend anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:27.63,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You really think you scream that I'm an idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:31.42,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,without making me want\Nto act like a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:36.89,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:42.82,Default,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,Safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:48.78,Default,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm not letting some\Nchick's boyfriend take me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:50.38,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:52.91,Default,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a sports club. You have no chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:05.03,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,High five!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:05.92,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,High five!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:09.93,sign_8804_102_The_End,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The End
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:12.93,sign_8885_103_Opening_Ceremony,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Opening Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:15.68,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,So, again, you better watch yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.68,sign_8942_104_Opening_Ceremony,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Opening Ceremony\N\N\N\N\N\NLong Homeroom \NOpening Ceremony \NShort Homeroom \NCleanup
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.68,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:21.06,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Suga-yan, is the soccer club busy\Nduring summer break?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:22.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:23.96,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,All rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:26.20,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We're planning to go to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You should come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:30.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Depends on club, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:30.32,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:32.32,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Chii-chan's supposed to come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:37.33,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:39.63,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shy about wearing a swimsuit and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:44.18,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So am I, but everyone's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:46.86,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ayaka-chan, Goda-kun, and Pattie, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:48.84,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:50.50,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So is Sugawara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:53.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:54.35,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:59.16,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kana, go make up with Chiaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:00.47,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:02.50,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Ch—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.68,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki, you guys are going\Nto the beach with us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:08.02,Default,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno, I'm thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it's okay if I come?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.11,Default,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:15.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Takano's coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:17.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it get awkward if I came?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:23.38,Default,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,I thrive on that awkwardness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:25.45,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sugawara-kun's not coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:27.10,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:29.06,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,He says it depends on his club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:30.38,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:33.43,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,So you two are coming for sure,\Nright, Yo-chan? Chii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:34.95,Default,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:41.22,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:44.77,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be weird trying to meet Chiaki\Nonce summer break starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:48.78,sign_11144_141_Uchimura_Chiaki,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Uchimura Chiaki
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:48.78,sign_11144_142_Today,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Today
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:48.78,sign_11144_143_Stay_behind_in_c,->,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here after class
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:48.78,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Will he agree to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.53,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, my battery's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:57.13,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:58.18,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Five, six, seven, eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:08:02.29,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's actually no club work\Nthat day. I {\i0}could{\i1} go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:06.10,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But going to the beach will make me\Nthink about Takano again,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:08.30,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,even though I know\Nthere's nothing between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:09.86,Flashback,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:11.80,Flashback,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't think anything of it, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:16.30,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'd just be miserable, going when\Nshe doesn't think anything of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:21.81,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't even say he read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:24.90,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Did Chiaki actually go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.07,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, can we practice here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:31.97,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Suga-yan, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.07,Default,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:35.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So are you going to the beach or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:37.32,Default,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:40.56,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It'll suck if Sugawara-kun doesn't come, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:46.71,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,You still like Sugawara-kun, Yo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:49.50,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:54.19,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I didn't have a chance to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:56.72,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:08:59.94,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:07.85,Italics,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Chiaki doesn't want\Nto patch things up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:12.56,Italics,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,He really did leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:15.61,Italics,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm going to be alone this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.24,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, that was a weird thing to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.80,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:25.26,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:32.75,Italics,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I'm always thinking\Nabout Sugawara-kun these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:39.80,Italics,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,And if Sugawara-kun doesn't\Ncome to the beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:44.81,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.11,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yo-cha—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:52.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Took you a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:53.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Were you doing something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:57.57,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't see my message?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:10:00.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, my battery died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:02.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for you,\Nso we could talk in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:03.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:05.37,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to patch things up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:10.38,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, we've broken up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:14.53,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong, Sugawara-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:16.71,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.07,0:10:18.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:20.14,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Practicing by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:23.47,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, Yo-chan's in the bathroom right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:24.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:28.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:30.64,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:36.31,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I didn't think you would\Nbreak up with me, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:38.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I got too comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:42.45,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If we patched things up now,\Nit would be like that never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:43.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It would feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:47.58,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think our relationship\Nwould last like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:49.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So let's break up properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:54.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Once that's done, I want to confess again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:03.36,Default,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I decided not to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:04.11,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:04.76,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Your club?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:09.27,Default,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I just don't really like\Nthat kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:11.16,Default,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,You're going, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:12.52,Default,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:15.15,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it'll be fun\Nif you aren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:23.36,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Try confessing, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.54,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,I'll reject you a hundred times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:27.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.05,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You better mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:30.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:34.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose you anymore, Kana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:36.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:40.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Please go out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:48.96,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:52.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Shucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:57.14,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to buy a swimsuit\Nfor the beach, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:03.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:23.36,Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Summer begins.
